sequenceDiagram
    participant Client as External Client
    participant KRBP as kube-rbac-proxy<br/>8443/TCP HTTPS TLS 1.2+
    participant VLLM as vLLM API Server<br/>8000/TCP HTTP
    participant Worker0 as HPU Worker (rank 0)<br/>Model Runner
    participant WorkerN as HPU Workers (ranks 1..N)<br/>Model Runners
    participant HPU as Gaudi HPU<br/>Accelerator
    participant Storage as Model Storage<br/>(PVC/S3)
    participant HFHub as HuggingFace Hub<br/>443/TCP HTTPS

    Note over Client,Storage: Flow 1: Model Inference Request
    Client->>KRBP: POST /v1/chat/completions<br/>Auth: Bearer Token / OpenShift OAuth
    KRBP->>KRBP: Validate token via<br/>Kubernetes RBAC
    KRBP->>VLLM: Forward request<br/>HTTP/8000 (localhost, plaintext)
    VLLM->>Worker0: Schedule inference<br/>In-process call
    Worker0->>HPU: Execute model forward pass<br/>PCIe/RDMA
    HPU-->>Worker0: Tensor output
    Worker0-->>VLLM: Generated tokens
    VLLM-->>KRBP: JSON Response (streaming or batch)
    KRBP-->>Client: HTTPS Response

    Note over Worker0,WorkerN: Flow 2: Multi-Card Tensor Parallel Inference
    Worker0->>WorkerN: Broadcast input tensors<br/>HCCL/TCP (dynamic ports, no encryption)
    WorkerN->>HPU: Execute model shard<br/>PCIe/RDMA
    HPU-->>WorkerN: Partial results
    WorkerN->>Worker0: HCCL all-reduce<br/>Aggregate partial results
    Worker0-->>VLLM: Combined output

    Note over Worker0,WorkerN: Flow 3: Disaggregated Prefill (NIXL)
    rect rgb(255, 245, 230)
        participant PrefillW as Prefill Worker
        participant DecodeW as Decode Worker
        PrefillW->>PrefillW: HPU→CPU KV cache copy
        PrefillW->>DecodeW: NIXL KV transfer<br/>RDMA/TCP (dynamic port, no encryption)
        DecodeW->>DecodeW: CPU→HPU KV cache copy
        DecodeW->>HPU: Continue decode with<br/>transferred KV cache
    end

    Note over VLLM,HFHub: Flow 4: Model Loading (Startup)
    VLLM->>Storage: Load model weights<br/>Filesystem (PVC) or HTTPS (S3)
    Storage-->>VLLM: Model artifacts
    VLLM->>HFHub: Download tokenizer/config (if not cached)<br/>HTTPS/443, TLS 1.2+, API Token (optional)
    HFHub-->>VLLM: Tokenizer files
    VLLM->>Worker0: Initialize model on HPU
    Worker0->>HPU: Load weights, compile HPU graphs<br/>Bucket-based compilation
    HPU-->>Worker0: Ready
